[22.948578, "o", "\r                                                                      \rlil bro thinks he's saving souls\r\n\u001b[4m120 BPM\u001b[0m is still too slow for this track\r\n Janji and Johnning need to rev up their \u001b[3mhyperactive\u001b[0m beats\r\n audiophile from temu would know that's not a good mix\r\nput the fries in the bag, sounds like they're serving stale tracks\r\nburnt down the kitchen with their subpar production skills\r\nneeds subway surfers gameplay to get those energy points up\r\ngng this is not it chief, no one wants to listen to this\r\ncaught in 4k, and now we're stuck watching mediocrity\r\nadding to cringe comp, because who even remembers Heroes Tonight?\r\nbefore GTA VI is crazy, at least that game has decent soundtracks\r\nsir this is a wendy's, Janji and Johnning are just phoning it in\r\ngenerational aura debt is insane, these producers owe us better tracks\r\nbro thinks he's him, but we all know who the real hero is - the one who makes good music\r\nNPC energy, like they're stuck on a never-ending loop of \"we're heroes tonight\"\r"]
[22.948738, "o", "\nstraight mid, because that's exactly what this track is - straight up boring\r\ncrashout behavior, and it looks like Janji and Johnning are crashing out too\r\n"]
[22.952194, "o", "\u001b_data@data-hp-14:~/Desktop/projects/trst\u001b\\"]
